* LICENCE information

MieruSDK consists of SimMips, LCD Simulator, MieruOS, MieruLib, sample
applications, and some utilities.
The simulators (SimMips and LCD Simulator, which are located on 'sim'
subdirectory) are dual licensed under the New BSD or GNU GPL Version 2
licenses. MieruOS, MieruLib, and the utilities (which are located on
'os', 'lib', and 'etc' subdirectories, respectively) are licensed under
the New BSD license. Sample applications have various licenses.

See COPYING files on the subdirectories for more information.

-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
* Abount MieruSDK

MieruSDK is a development kit that includes a simple operating system and 
simulators and some tools for MieruPC. 

** MieruPC
This is a small FPGA-based computer system.
For more information, please access the web site.
http://www.mierupc.com/

** MieruOS
This is a simple operating system running on MieruPC written in C++. 

** SimMips
This is a MIPS system simulator written in C++ and is originally developed in
Tokyo Institute of Technology. For more information, please access the web site.
http://www.arch.cs.titech.ac.jp/SimMips/
I have modified the SimMips to emulate MieruPC by implementing specific 
functions for it.

** LCD Simulator
This is a simulator for MieruLCD written in GDK and C. It's possible to emulate
full environment of MieruPC to use both LCD Simulator and modified SimMips.

-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
* Development with MieruSDK for MieruPC

See doc/mierusdk.txt for the explanation to develop your own applications 
for MieruPC.

